DIN 2014 Stencil is a stencil version of DIN 2014 typeface inspired by signage, data plates and stencilled building inscriptions. The typeface has a pronounced industrial spirit and can be used in the most rigorous conditions. The typeface was designed by Vasily Biryukov and released by Paratype in 2017. The demo version of the font is prepared exclusively for testing on www.paratype.com and www.axis-praxis.org. Copying and distribution is prohibited.
